metadata.name: Shear Valla
metadata.description:
"What causes horror is desire, and desire becomes monster.
In appearance, Shear looks like an ordinary woman, but in reality, she's a Succubus.
His madness is matched only by his hunger..."

"I'm hungry... hungry... HUNGRY!!"

Shear Valla is the first piece of this collection

After purchase you can contact me for all downloadable files. Includes : full resolution & alternative versions.
